arrays (a three-dimensional array), then my tests are not recognized.  I
already know I can&#39;t use an array of Maps, as I originally wanted,
because Java5 isn&#39;t able to cast a HashMap back to an Object when it&#39;s
doing its generics thing (although I&#39;m kind of fuzzy on the details).
